        Return an iterator through the elements of ``self``.
        Not implemented in general.

        EXAMPLES::

            sage: sage.rings.ring.Ring.__iter__(ZZ)
            Traceback (most recent call last):
            ...
            NotImplementedError: object does not support iteration
        """
